::KitKat::

She looked at Quickstrike and at Stringtra.  Her ears pulled back and still 
ready to fight, she backed up a few feet.  She was brave, but not stupid to 
take on two bots at once.  Well, not when she was dmamaged.  She stopped 
growling.
"Now will someone tell me what that spotted thing was.  I smelt Maximal from 
it. That's why I attacked.  Who are you two? Whom do you serve?"
She didn't really care who they worked for.  All she really wanted was to 
use a CR chamber for a bit and be on her way.
